name: James DeSau
text: I miss working at this location, great team and leadership. Even ordered as a customer and the food was always exquisite.

name: Benice Ryan Balague
text: Great pizza and Cinnabon! Great service and very helpful staff. Thank you again! You know who you are!

name: Tony Ramos
text: Horrendous service. I ordered my pizza at 2 to be able to pick up at 6:45 I had to wait approximately 20 minutes after my pick up time you received a burnt pizza and calzone.

name: Shelly Campos Chan
text: We did curbside pick up and followed the instructions posted on the front window we were told it’d be a 5 minute wait and we were waiting for 30 minutes kept calling the place and no one picked up. Terrible customer service

name: Stephen Patton
text: This place is good! Reasonable rates, considerable dishes and the employees are always very welcoming.

name: Charla James
text: Typically when I order a pizza from here it's fantastic, however, this afternoon, the crust was so thin, the slices were completely limp, it didn't taste good, it covered my hands in sauce, I was livid. The toppings were literally dripping …More

name: Michael Sanderson
text: I'll have to make sure to stop giving such decent tips if my pie is going to show up thrown into the box and nearly folded over on itself. Besides that if this were 10 years ago I'd have never paid for one of your pizzas, your delivery area is small, need a bit more efficiency

name: Scott Juskowiak
text: It's a Pizza Hut, nothing out of the ordinary here.

name: Analise Powell
text: Great pizza, amazing service from the GM.

name: Haydar Moe
text: It took me 15 min to find it... ordered carryout online, the address on Pizza Hut website was wrong. the quality is just okay. Do not expect to get good costumer service from this place.  I'm done with Pizza Hut.

name: William Summers
text: I thought the staff made a mistake on my pizza but come to find out I was the one mistaken. Aidan, the shift manager, was great about making sure it was all taken care of and the situation was rectified. Even though it was my mistake! Stellar service, good pizza, good experience.

name: L Hardman
text: Pretty quick on getting your order done.  Wish the had seating so you could eat there.  It just a pick-up store.  The are really friendly there

name: Tyler E
text: Wouldn't deliver to me even though I'm less than 1/2 a mile away! The pizza was great, but they need to work out their delivery situation for more than 3 stars in my book.

name: J Mo
text: This location does not do any sort of quality checks. Multiple times I have received raw/under-cooked pizza/p’zones.

name: Adam Bloomfield
text: Sat on hold for 10 mins then got hung up on. After I called back it went to an automated answering service. Waste of time for trash pizza.

name: Haylee Hilderbrand
text: The food was good. However, my delivery guy dropped one of my items and offered to go back and get more. I ended up waiting almost an hour before he got back with my item. I kept calling to check and make sure they were bringing them and it was a different excuse both times I called.

name: OrbitalFFA
text: Very nice drivers, will keep ordering!!

name: Adventure Mckinley
text: Giving it a go!

name: suo toshiro
text: Need more staff

name: T W S
text: Go pizza but no where to sit down and eat.

name: David Ruff
text: Fair pizza. Take out only.

name: Jack
text: It was esquisite

name: Melissa Zindle
text: This is the second time pizza hut has got my family sick at this location
